detaileddescription.para: Panorama's layout make it impractical to support iterators as defined by Faiss (i.e. InvertedListsIterator API). The iterator would require to allocate and reassemble the vector at each call. Hence, we override this method to throw an error, this effectively disables the iterate_codes and iterate_codes_range methods.
